{"tid":2448031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共要求引渡協助許智峯的國會議員 被丹麥政府拒絕","createTime":"2021-03-15T15:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T23:42:23.000Z","uid":5195,"like":108,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"026fdefc9cf2c09109d1d1c5df4b3329350a7be6","tid":2448031,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:23:21.000Z","msg":"前立法會議員許智峯於去年11底月離港前往丹麥，他未有按保釋條件返港，並宣布不再回港，目前被警方通緝。《德國之聲》今天（15日）報道，港府早前尋求丹麥政府協助，要求引渡協助許智峯到丹麥的國會議員Uffe Elb&aelig;k和Katarina Ammitzb&oslash;ll到港，更發出國際逮捕令，惟有關要求已被丹麥政府拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n《德國之聲》引述丹麥《政治報》報道，指港府向丹麥政府要求，引渡協助許智峯到丹麥的國會議員Uffe Elb&aelig;k和Katarina Ammitzb&oslash;ll到港，更發出國際逮捕令，不過有關要求已被丹麥政府拒絕；報道又引述，丹麥情報機關已向兩名議員發出警示，要求他們暫時不要前往任何與中國簽署引渡條約的國家或地區。<br />\n<br />\n01唔貼link"},{"pid":"1bb5d293efe4e3478be7b968d6daff604f6efed5","tid":2448031,"uid":13745,"like":17,"dislike":6,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:24:08.000Z","msg":"點解唔通緝大灣暉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b090b1e3bfbe68e87947c13ea984788006ce5a","tid":2448031,"uid":58841,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"屌好心港共咪撚咁弱智啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要人地國家交自己國民出黎係咪食撚左屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e17af172383546204373a011f184eae4f662371","tid":2448031,"uid":51583,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"佢地有引渡協議咩？<br />\n就算有都唔會ON99攪自己議員啦"},{"pid":"5751ee3f05b3fc1839eabc51da26dc3c8baad6c0","tid":2448031,"uid":194483,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:26:08.000Z","msg":"咁樣都唔知要引渡幾多國際政要喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae618d4f9f6131f310c12bfbb34b3e8e600f94e2","tid":2448031,"uid":47775,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:26:52.000Z","m